metadata.name: Terrifying Cute
metadata.description:
I wake up, I go to school, I learn something, I go home, I don't do homework, I play for a little, I go to sleep.

I wake up, I go to school, I get bullied, I go home, I do homework, I play for a little, I go to sleep.

I wake up, I go to school, I learn something, I go home, I do homework, Parents are getting a divorce, I go to sleep.

I wake up, I go to school, I learn something, I go home, I don't do homework, I cry for a little, I go to sleep.

I wake up, I don't go to school, I learn something, I play games, I clean my room, I talk to parents, I go to sleep.

I wake up, I go to school, I don't learn anything, I go home, I do homework, Dad is moving out, I go to sleep.

I wake up, I go to school, I learn something, I go home, I do homework, I play for a little, I go to sleep.

I wake up, I don't go to school, I learn something, I hug mum, I do homework, I play for a little, I go to sleep.

I WAKE UP.
